<ul>
  <li>
    <p><a href="/styleguidetemplate/mktg/company-terminology/#capitalize-human">Make sure to properly capitalize HUMAN and HUMANâ€™s product names.</a></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><a href="/styleguidetemplate/mktg/company-terminology/#product-names">Donâ€™t abbreviate HUMANâ€™s product names.</a></p>
  </li>
</ul>

<h3 id="grammar"><a href="/styleguidetemplate/mktg/grammar/">Grammar</a></h3>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p><a href="/styleguidetemplate/mktg/grammar/#active-and-passive-voice">Use the active voice whenever possible.</a></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><a href="/styleguidetemplate/mktg/grammar/#singular-they">Use the singular <em>they</em> as a gender-neutral pronoun.</a></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><a href="/styleguidetemplate/mktg/grammar/#american-english">Use standard American English spelling conventions.</a></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><a href="/styleguidetemplate/mktg/grammar/#present-tense">Use the present tense whenever possible.</a></p>
  </li>
</ul>

<h3 id="punctuation"><a href="/styleguidetemplate/mktg/punctuation/">Punctuation</a></h3>

<ul>
  <li><a href="/styleguidetemplate/mktg/punctuation/#serial-commas">Use serial commas.</a></li>
</ul>

<h3 id="tone-and-content"><a href="/styleguidetemplate/mktg/tone-and-content/">Tone and content</a></h3>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p><a href="/styleguidetemplate/mktg/tone-and-content/#be-friendly">Strive for an approachable, friendly tone.</a></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><a href="/styleguidetemplate/mktg/tone-and-content/#write-for-non-experts">Write for a broad audience, not just for experts.</a></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><a href="/styleguidetemplate/mktg/tone-and-content/#filler-words">Avoid filler words.</a></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><a href="/styleguidetemplate/mktg/tone-and-content/#simple-vs.-complex">Try to use short, simple words instead of complex, abstract words.</a></p>
  </li>
</ul>

<h3 id="formatting-and-organization"><a href="/styleguidetemplate/mktg/formatting-and-organization/">Formatting and organization</a></h3>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p><a href="/styleguidetemplate/mktg/formatting-and-organization/#captions">Put captions after their associated image.</a></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><a href="/styleguidetemplate/mktg/formatting-and-organization/#descriptive-link-text">Use descriptive link text.</a></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><a href="/styleguidetemplate/mktg/formatting-and-organization/#title-capitalization">Use title case for titles.</a></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><a href="/styleguidetemplate/mktg/formatting-and-organization/#heading-capitalization">Use sentence case for headings.</a></p>
  </li>
</ul>

